name: Present
effect: Ranged. Roll 1 Die to determine this Move's Power. Roll 2 Dice and use the higher result if Snow Weather is active or during the month of December. If a 4-6 is rolled by this move's Effect the target recovers 1 HP after damage calculation. -1 Accuracy.
description: The user approaches its foe and gives it a lovely present that may be nice or may be a prank.
